# .gitignore — idea-to-production marketplace
#
# Surgical, not blanket. Two directories hold BOTH tracked assets and runtime
# cruft, so they are never ignored wholesale:
#   .claude/   → agent-memory/ is a tracked ledger; only runtime files are ignored below.
#   .foundry/  → MARKETPLACE_SCORECARD.jsonl + governance.md are tracked; never ignore this dir.
# Inspection reports are tracked ONLY when archived under doc/historical/, so their
# ignore rules are root-anchored (a leading /) to leave the archives addable.

# --- Claude Code harness runtime (per-machine / per-session, never shared) ---
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
.claude/cache/
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- Marketplace self-dogfood + lifecycle runtime artifacts (regenerable/transient) ---
# These appear at the repo root when the marketplace's own scripts run against itself.
# The durable ledgers (.foundry/MARKETPLACE_SCORECARD.jsonl, doc/historical/*) stay tracked.
/SCORECARD.json
/marketplace-health.json
/IN_PROGRESS.md
/CHECKPOINT_*.md
/.i2p/
/*_INSPECTION_REPORT.md

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
*~
*.swp
*.swo
.idea/

# --- ComfyUI model-survey artifacts (generated rasters retained on disk, never in git) ---
# catalog.md, journal.jsonl, manifest.json, and comfyui-model-survey.pdf stay TRACKED (the durable record);
# only the large/regenerable images are ignored. Root-anchored to scope them to this one tree.
/doc/comfyui-experiment/images/
/doc/comfyui-experiment/thumbs/
/doc/comfyui-experiment/contact-sheets/
/doc/comfyui-experiment/.catalog-raw.pdf

# --- Language tooling (defensive: plugins drive local node/python test runs) ---
node_modules/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
coverage/
.coverage
*.log
.playwright-mcp/
_render_*.html

# image-craft-study: track ledgers/catalogs/curated-JSON; ignore large/regenerable rasters
/doc/image-craft-study/corpus/genres/
/doc/image-craft-study/corpus/styles/
/doc/image-craft-study/corpus/scenes/
/doc/image-craft-study/corpus/diagrams/
/doc/image-craft-study/corpus/landscapes/
/doc/image-craft-study/corpus/action/
/doc/image-craft-study/workflows/raw/
/doc/image-craft-study/craft/images/
/doc/image-craft-study/craft/thumbs/
/doc/image-craft-study/craft/contact-sheets/
/doc/image-craft-study/craft/validate/
/doc/image-craft-study/verification/new/
/doc/image-craft-study/verification/old/
/doc/image-craft-study/rig-inventory/awesome-contact.jpg
/doc/image-craft-study/rig-inventory/awesome-recipes.txt
# toolchain (Phase 8): track src/ scripts + the small proof/ evidence; ignore frames + heavy intermediates
/doc/image-craft-study/toolchain/frames/
/doc/image-craft-study/toolchain/out/
/doc/image-craft-study/toolchain/src/*.png
